{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpRule\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkLatticeOpRule</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rhs</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">op</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">Meta.Sym.BackwardRule</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Build a reusable backward rule decomposing `pre ⊑ op … s⃗` for a lattice operator. The operator's\nvalue arguments are made schematic; `rewrites` saturate the operator through its distribution and\nunfolding equalities, the terminal keyed by the reduced head fires, and any state arguments left\nover-applied by the terminal are point-framed onto the precondition. When the reduced head has no\nregistered terminal, the saturated `pre ⊑ reduced` is handed back as the sole subgoal. Throws when the\noperator neither reduces nor has a terminal, since its rule would be the identity.\n\nFor `⊓`, produces `∀ a b s⃗ pre, pre ⊑ a s⃗ → pre ⊑ b s⃗ → pre ⊑ (a ⊓ b) s⃗`. For the opaque residual\n`upperAdjoint f b`, produces `∀ f b s⃗ pre, f (fun u⃗ => ⌜u⃗ = s⃗⌝ ⊓ pre) ⊑ b → pre ⊑ upperAdjoint f b s⃗`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpRule","kind":"def","line":135,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpRule","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L135-L183"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpTable\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkLatticeOpTable</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">frameSplits</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Std.HashMap\">Std.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Std.HashMap\">Std.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The lattice-split table keyed by operator head, merging the built-in connectives with the\nregistered frame operators' splits. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpTable","kind":"def","line":56,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkLatticeOpTable","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L56-L60"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.builtinLatticeOps\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">builtinLatticeOps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The built-in connective splits, whose rewrites and terminals seed every saturation. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.builtinLatticeOps","kind":"def","line":52,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.builtinLatticeOps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L52-L54"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.upperAdjoint\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">LatticeOp</span>.<span class=\"name\">upperAdjoint</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The magic-wand residual `upperAdjoint f b`: point-framed, closes with `le_upperAdjoint`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.upperAdjoint","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.upperAdjoint","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L47-L50"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.top\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">LatticeOp</span>.<span class=\"name\">top</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The lattice top `⊤`: distributes via `top_apply`, closes with `le_top`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.top","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.top","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L44-L46"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.ofProp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">LatticeOp</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofProp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The pure assertion `⌜·⌝`: distributes via `ofProp_apply`, closes with the `⊤`-fixed\n`top_le_ofProp`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.ofProp","kind":"def","line":39,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.ofProp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L39-L43"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.himp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">LatticeOp</span>.<span class=\"name\">himp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/FrameProc.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp\">LatticeOp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Heyting implication `⇨`: distributes via `himp_apply`, closes with `le_himp`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.himp","kind":"def","line":36,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.LatticeOp.himp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/LatticeOp.lean#L3